{"word":"Sabbatic Year","slug":"sabbatic-year","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sabbatic Year</b> A rest recurring every seventh year.<br/> Called Year of Release<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=9'>Deu 15:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=10'>Deu 31:10</a><br/> Ordinances concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=11'>Exo 23:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25'>Lev 25</a><br/> Israelitish bondservants set free in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=2'>Exo 21:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=12'>Deu 15:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=34&verse=14'>Jer 34:14</a><br/> Creditors required to release debtors in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=6'>Deu 15:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=18'>Deu 15:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=31'>Neh 10:31</a><br/> Ordinances concerning instruction in the law during<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=13'>Deu 31:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=18'>Neh 8:18</a><br/> Punishment to follow violation of the ordinances concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=41'>Lev 26:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=34&verse=22'>Jer 34:22</a><br/><a href='S:Jubilee'>Jubilee</a>"}]}